      "props": {
        "text": "GET /feed.xml returns valid Atom XML. Each entry carries the scenario text, agent count, round count, total events, quality data, and a direct link. Public sims link to /share/<id>; private ones link to the internal view. 60s cache header keeps feed readers from hammering the endpoint."
